{"tid":1073132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜訪港再失言：阿爾卑斯山旁的不丹人都傻傻的","createTime":"2019-03-22T12:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T04:35:23.000Z","uid":134071,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"101bec80318cb925dc26f4b60125c44886f67a07","tid":1073132,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:48:58.000Z","msg":"阿爾卑斯山係歐洲， 不丹係亞洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1553255415.A.7DA.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1553255415.A.7DA.html&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1xphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=86a706e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1553255415.A.7DA.html</a><br />\n時間Fri Mar 22 19:50:12 2019<br />\n1.媒體來源:<br />\n三立<br />\n2.完整新聞標題:<br />\n離譜！韓國瑜訪港再失言：阿爾卑斯山旁的不丹人都傻傻的<br />\n<br />\n3.完整新聞內文:<br />\n政治中心／綜合報導<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜今（22）展開出訪行程，首站抵達香港。此行韓國瑜雖打著經濟為主之名，然而卻到處充滿了政治意涵，與香港特首林鄭月娥的握手畫面，就引起台灣社會很大的議論。韓國瑜在香港看來心情相當不錯，然而不知是不是太嗨了，又再度爆出失言與歧視爭議。<br />\n<br />\n臉書粉絲專頁「肯腦濕的人生相談室」貼出了一段影片，影片中韓國瑜致詞時，首先感謝現場人士稱讚台灣的快樂指數從第25名上升到第1名，然而說著說著，他竟脫口「在我印象中，最快樂的國家吼，大概是在阿爾卑斯山旁邊，像不丹，與世無爭，居民都傻傻的，很單純，隨便有個麵包吃就覺得自己全世界最快樂」。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的言論一出，引起眾人譁然，除了地理觀念缺乏以外，繼上次爆出菲律賓「瑪莉亞」失言後，第二次爆出歧視言論。不少網友紛紛表示很傻眼，有人就說「不丹傻傻的？你算甚麼？」、「這人真的自我感覺良好到很奇葩」、「支那了不起？」、「貴族學校創辦人怎麼這麼low」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KensTalking/videos/2312539278981776/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKensTalking%2Fvideos%2F2312539278981776%2F&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1xphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=bf96cffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KensTalking/videos/2312539278981776/</a><br />\n<br />\n4.完整新聞連結 (或短網址):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=516170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D516170&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1xphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=4a3af3ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D516170&h=371c5fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=516170</a>"},{"pid":"80f31d940826de2deb6233c203526bf4caa48c4e","tid":1073132,"uid":27608,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a2524efaaa90280c2ca43cec606411aeb51df1","tid":1073132,"uid":53672,"like":127,"dislike":2,"score":125,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"所以話台仔真係on9，選個咁既9up佬去做市長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果蓋清係台仔分分鐘都做到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e528186838a9694511925ece91b5306351e44d","tid":1073132,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"g持韓國瑜代表國民黨參選總統"},{"pid":"a3076218b4e091fc679d5588d21054280233bbe1","tid":1073132,"uid":209225,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"24a2524efaaa90280c2ca43cec606411aeb51df1","tid":1073132,"uid":53672,"like":127,"dislike":2,"score":125,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"所以話台仔真係on9，選個咁既9up佬去做市長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果蓋清係台仔分分鐘都做到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i